API v1 profile
==============

Our representations follow the standards from:
* JSON API: http://jsonapi.org/
* JSON-stat: http://json-stat.org/

The accepted media-type in all our representations is either `application/json`
or `application/vnd.api+json`.
Representations in other formats (e.g. `text/csv`) are also supported on a
case-by-case basis.

